            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the tortiglioni for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the tortiglioni, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-4-1706541661439-x200.jpg",
