    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p>",
